# Action descriptions
desc-basic-synthesis = Increases progress. Efficiency: 100 (120 after Lv.31).
desc-basic-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 100.
desc-masters-mend = Restores 30 durability.
desc-hasty-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 100, costs no CP, success rate: 60%.
desc-rapid-synthesis = Increases progress. Efficiency: 250 (500 after Lv.63), success rate: 50%.
desc-observe = Skips a turn. Used to combo Focused Synthesis and Focused Touch.
desc-tricks-of-the-trade = Restores 20 CP. Only available when condition is Good or Excellent.
desc-waste-not = Reduces durability loss by 50% for the next 4 steps.
desc-veneration = Increases the efficiency of progress actions by 50% for the next 4 steps.
desc-standard-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 125. Combo with Basic Touch reduces CP cost.
desc-great-strides = Doubles the efficiency of the next touch action. Active for 3 steps.
desc-innovation = Increases the efficiency of quality actions by 50% for the next 4 steps.
desc-final-appraisal = Stops progress just before completion when using a progress action. Active for 5 steps.
desc-waste-not-ii = Reduces durability loss by 50% for the next 8 steps.
desc-byregot-s-blessing = Consumes Inner Quiet stacks to increase quality. Efficiency 100~300, +20 per stack.
desc-precise-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 150, grants 2 stacks of Inner Quiet. Only available when condition is Good or Excellent.
desc-muscle-memory = Only available on the first step. Increases progress. Efficiency: 300. Doubles the effect of the next progress action. Active for 5 steps.
desc-careful-synthesis = Increases progress. Efficiency: 150 (180 after Lv.82).
desc-manipulation = Restores 5 durability after each step for the next 8 steps.
desc-prudent-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 100, costs only 5 durability. Cannot be used under Waste Not.
desc-reflect = Only available on the first step. Increases quality. Efficiency: 300, grants 2 stacks of Inner Quiet.
desc-preparatory-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 200, grants 2 stacks of Inner Quiet, costs 20 durability.
desc-groundwork = Increases progress. Efficiency: 300 (360 after Lv.86), costs 20 durability. Efficiency halved when durability is insufficient.
desc-delicate-synthesis = Increases progress and quality. Efficiency: 100 (progress efficiency 150 after Lv.94).
desc-intensive-synthesis = Increases progress. Efficiency: 400. Only available when condition is Good or Excellent.
desc-trained-eye = Only available on the first step when recipe level is 10+ levels lower. Increases quality by 100% of maximum.
desc-advanced-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 150. Combo with Standard Touch reduces CP cost.
desc-prudent-synthesis = Increases progress. Efficiency: 180, costs only 5 durability. Cannot be used under Waste Not.
desc-trained-finesse = Only available with 10 stacks of Inner Quiet. Increases quality. Efficiency: 100, costs no durability.
desc-careful-observation = Consumes 1 Crafter's Delineation to change condition. Up to 3 uses per craft. Simulator UI does not currently support condition switching.
desc-heart-and-soul = Consumes 1 Crafter's Delineation to allow one use of Precise Touch, Intensive Synthesis, or Tricks of the Trade. Up to 1 use per craft.
desc-refined-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 100. Combo with Basic Touch grants an additional stack of Inner Quiet.
desc-daring-touch = Increases quality. Efficiency: 150, costs no CP, success rate: 60%.
desc-immaculate-mend = Restores durability to maximum.
desc-quick-innovation = Grants Innovation status. Lasts 1 step. Up to 1 use per craft.
desc-trained-perfection = The next action that consumes durability will cost 0 durability. Up to 1 use per craft.
desc-stellar-steady-hand = Guarantees the next action will succeed. Active for 3 steps.

